<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>judul</title>
    <link href="/style/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="p-10 text-center bg-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl p-6 mx-auto mt-12 bg-white shadow-md rounded-xl">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Import Data Kinerja</h2>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <label class="block mb-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700" for="file">
                Pilih file (CSV atau Excel)
            </label>
            <input type="file" name="file" id="file" accept=".csv, .xlsx"
                class="block w-full text-sm text-gray-900 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg cursor-pointer bg-gray-50" />
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 mb-6 text-sm text-gray-600 bg-gray-100 border border-gray-300 border-dashed rounded-md">
            <strong>Format kolom yang diharuskan:</strong>
            <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside">
                <li><code>Nama Dosen</code></li>
                <li><code>Judul Penelitian</code> / <code>Judul Pengabdian</code> / <code>Judul Publikasi</code></li>
                <li><code>Tahun</code></li>
                <li><code>Jenis</code> (misal: Penelitian Dasar, Publikasi Jurnal, dll)</li>
                <li><code>Skor Kinerja</code> (opsional)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <button type="submit" class="px-5 py-2 text-white transition bg-blue-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700">
                Import Data
            </button>
            <a href="/dashboard" class="text-gray-600 hover:underline hover:text-gray-800">
                ‚Üê Kembali ke Dashboard
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>